An unknown voice disturbed me while I was levitating during my cultivation to reach the transcendent demonic state.
My concentration had been broken, and I fell into an unconscious, overloaded state. When I awoke a month later, the Lich King had already taken control of the Murim.
After the battle that ended with the destruction of the Heavenly Demon Cult, I awoke a hundred and forty years later in a Murim where magic and martial arts coexisted.
Qiandao 30 Tian Yi Quan Bao Xing

Invasion of gods from other world, Ten thousand saviors were selected to enter the secret realm, where the bloodthirsty battles against demonic beasts are streamed live for the whole world to see.
Chu Mo: Are you crazy? Except me, all the saviors are immortals. How am I supposed to fight a demonic beast, Is this reasonable?
"The sign-in system is activated. " On the first day of sign-in, You will get the power of the thousand-year-old demonic beast. On the second day of sign-in, You will gain the battle experience of the legendary God of War. After 30 days of signing in, I can explode the stars with one punch!
(Source: Bilibili, translated)
